Class SkipLocaleForStringContentTemplateLookupStrategy

  • java.lang.Object

  • public class SkipLocaleForStringContentTemplateLookupStrategy
extends freemarker.cache.TemplateLookupStrategy
    Ogham special TemplateLookupStrategy that is used in order to skip Locale resolution for templates that are provided directly by a string and not by a path.
